29 the department’s rules and regulations. Furthermore, the department shall provide funding for child
30 care for eligible staff providing early intervention services at least twenty (20) hours per week to
31 infants and toddlers with developmental delays and disabilities under Part C of the Individuals with
32 Disabilities Education Act. Eligibility is limited to qualifying childcare educators and childcare
33 staff with family incomes up to three hundred percent (300%) of the applicable federal poverty
34 guidelines and for child care assistance for these children will fall under the federal Child Care
