1 This act would eliminate the sunset on the provision of funding for child care for eligible
2 child care educators and child care staffs, remove the family income limit, and would expand the
3 program to include staff providing early intervention services to infants and toddlers with
4 developmental delays and disabilities and would require an annual reporting of participant data to
5 the governor and general assembly by November 1.
6 This act would take effect upon passage.
